        "notes": "Citizens of all countries in the globe are eligible for Tourist eVisa (VT). Options: single entry 30 days (USD 62) or single entry 90 days (USD 152). Processing time: 3 business days. Passport must be valid for at least 6 months from intended entry date. Validity runs from the intended entry date. Extensions available online (up to 15 days past expiry) or in person at ICS Head Office Addis Ababa (beyond 15 days). Extension fees: 30-day extension USD 102; 90-day extension USD 302.",
